OL,3,CDozens face Christmas on city's
OL,4,Cstreets after rise in rough sleeping
OL,6,FHomelessness charities in Sheffield
OL,7,Fsay they are seeing record numbers of
OL,8,Fpeople sleeping rough in the run up to
OL,9,FChristmas.
OL,11,FThe city has one of the highest rates
OL,12,Fof street homelessness outside of
OL,13,FLondon, with the latest statistics
OL,14,Fshowing a rise of 72% in the past year.
OL,16,FIn June 2024, on a single night, there
OL,17,Fwere 62 rough sleepers on the streets
OL,18,Fof Sheffield.
