OL,3,CDozens face Christmas on city's
OL,4,Cstreets after rise in rough sleeping
OL,6,FITV News Calendar joined charity
OL,7,FFramework's outreach team on their pre-
OL,8,Fdawn patrol of the city in the run up
OL,9,Fto Christmas.
OL,11,FThe organisation carry out the walk
OL,12,Fevery single day of the year and say
OL,13,Fthey have seen a big rise in demand
OL,14,Frecently.
OL,16,FManager of the charity's Sheffield
OL,17,Fteam Steph Haines said: "It's gone up
OL,18,Frapidly I'd say over the last two
OL,19,Fyears and it just keeps growing. Our
OL,20,Fclients as well do seem to have very
OL,21,Fcomplex needs.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G2/11
