OL,3,CDozens face Christmas on city's
OL,4,Cstreets after rise in rough sleeping
OL,6,F"The mental health seems to be getting
OL,7,Fworse, substance misuse is getting
OL,8,Fworse and people are out here for a
OL,9,Flong time. So the associated problems
OL,10,Fseem to spiral."
OL,12,FAlex Woolfenden is a former client of
OL,13,Fthe Framework team - he spent three
OL,14,Fyears sleeping rough but has now been
OL,15,Fhoused for about 18 months.
