OL,3,CDozens face Christmas on city's
OL,4,Cstreets after rise in rough sleeping
OL,6,FHe said: "Frankly it's terrifying,
OL,7,Fespecially for someone like me, I'm a
OL,8,Fbit of a loner. It's about as bad as
OL,9,Fyou can imagine, trying to find
OL,10,Fsomewhere that's safe, trying to find
OL,11,Fsomewhere that's quiet but not too
OL,12,Fquiet"
OL,14,F"In winter it's freezing. You try and
OL,15,Ffind squats or buildings if you can,
OL,16,Fbut if not then there's a real health
OL,17,Frisk."
