OL,3,CDozens face Christmas on city's
OL,4,Cstreets after rise in rough sleeping
OL,6,FFramework say a rise in the use of
OL,7,Fsuper-strength drugs are exacerbating
OL,8,Fthe problem of rough sleeping across
OL,9,Fthe UK, not just in Sheffield.
OL,11,FDuring the outreach patrol, they came
OL,12,Facross a man laying unconscious inside
OL,13,Fa multi-storey carpark - who they
OL,14,Fsuspect is under the influence of
OL,15,Fstrong drugs.
OL,17,FSteph Haines said: "At the minute
OL,18,Fthere's some really strong drugs going
OL,19,Faround. Obviously there's been the
OL,20,Frise of fentanyl, but there's another
OL,21,Ftype of drug called nitazines.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G5/11
