OL,3,CDozens face Christmas on city's
OL,4,Cstreets after rise in rough sleeping
OL,6,F"They're really really potent - I
OL,7,Fthink they're about 100 times stronger
OL,8,Fthan fentanyl. So a lot of the time
OL,9,Fwhen we come across someone who's
OL,10,Fseemingly asleep, it's really
OL,11,Fimportant we check they're breathing."
OL,13,FThe Archer Project, which is based
OL,14,Fbehind the Cathedral in Sheffield, has
OL,15,Falso seen a spike in demand recently.
OL,17,FThe charity provides breakfasts and
OL,18,Flunches for rough sleepers and engages
OL,19,Fwith those on the streets to help get
OL,20,Fthem into housing.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G6/11
