OL,3,CDozens face Christmas on city's
OL,4,Cstreets after rise in rough sleeping
OL,6,FHe said: "It's very difficult at the
OL,7,Fmoment because I have to balance life.
OL,8,FSo I've got somebody, we sleep on the
OL,9,Fstreets together, he keeps my stuff on
OL,10,Fhim so I can go to work, I then pretty
OL,11,Fmuch go to work, come back and we
OL,12,Fsleep outside so for the last three
OL,13,Fmonths I've been sleeping on concrete.
OL,15,F"It's very difficult because it's a
OL,16,Ffull time role. You've got to sleep
OL,17,Fwith one eye open"
