OL,3,CDozens face Christmas on city's
OL,4,Cstreets after rise in rough sleeping
OL,6,FChief Executive of the Archer Project
OL,7,FTim Renshaw said the rise leaves the
OL,8,Forganisation struggling to keep people
OL,9,Foff the streets.
OL,11,FHe said: "Really that tests the whole
OL,12,Fsystem. If we're not moving people
OL,13,Faway from the street into first ever
OL,14,Faccomodation or further then all the
OL,15,Fsystem feels busy. And we can't do
OL,16,Fthose really important things like
OL,17,Frelationship build with a small group
OL,18,Fof people which actually helps people
OL,19,Fmove on into a better life."
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G9/11
