OL,3,CDozens face Christmas on city's
OL,4,Cstreets after rise in rough sleeping
OL,6,FThe rise in rough sleeping has put
OL,7,Fpressure on support services - both
OL,8,FFramework and Archer Project are
OL,9,Fhaving to fundraise to keep operating.
OL,11,FThe government this week announced #1
OL,12,Fbillion of extra support for councils
OL,13,Fto tackle homelessness, #48 million of
OL,14,Fwhich is for Yorkshire and the Humber.
OL,16,FDeputy Prime Minister Angela Raynor
OL,17,Fsaid: "I am determined to break the
OL,18,Fcycle of spiralling homelessness and
OL,19,Fget back on track to ending it for
OL,20,Fgood.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1        G10/11
