OL,6,F"This largest-ever investment marks a
OL,7,Fturning point, giving councils the
OL,8,Ftools they need to act quickly and put
OL,9,Fin place support for people to tackle,
OL,10,Freduce and prevent homelessness. It's
OL,11,Ftime to turn the tide."
